		<title>הכירו את&#8230; michel25!</title>
		<link>http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/?p=4136&amp;utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=%25d7%2594%25d7%259b%25d7%2599%25d7%25a8%25d7%2595-%25d7%2590%25d7%25aa-michel25</link>
